        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Track your interviews effortlessly</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-left max-w-xs mx-auto">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
